{
  "stem": "188.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 459.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we're told, once they see the other, we'll go to another-- to another house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And these were farmers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "One-- this was the family Oosterfeld and they were wonderful people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I pleaded with them, and I begged them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I said, you cannot separate us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Please do not separate us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I have promised my parents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] They consented to keep both of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we were told that there is a bedroom.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There is a little girl in the bed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Just crawl in bed with her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we spent six months there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I remember, my brother, every night-- he was so little-- and every night he would say-- we would go to bed together, and he would say, Milie, [DUTCH], which means 'hold me.' And I would.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we would say our Hebrew prayer that I had learned in-- in Hebrew school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And for some reason, I guess I felt that was, at that time, my link to being Jewish.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And we would whisper it at night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And we had a certain freedom there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We were allowed on the farm.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I was allowed to help.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I learned how to plant potatoes, how to scrub floors, how to do all sorts of things that I didn't know I could do.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "It wasn't until fairly recently that I discovered that the family Oosterfeld never took a penny as-- for our stay with them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They were unbelievable parent-- people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I-- as a slip of the tongue, I call them parents.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And I'm still in contact with Mrs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Oosterfeld, and she's been here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And she has been recognized as a righteous Gentile.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
